      Access BIOS
    </h4>

    <ol class="govuk-list govuk-list--number">
      <li>From the Windows Start menu, select the power icon</li>
      <li>Hold down &lsquo;Shift&rsquo; and select &lsquo;Restart&rsquo;</li>
