      and storing your passwords.
    </p>

    <ol class="govuk-list govuk-list--number">
      <li>Enter the BIOS password (case sensitive)</li>
      <li>Select the &lsquo;Security&rsquo; menu and the option that resembles &lsquo;Administrator Password&rsquo;</li>
      <li>If asked, enter the current BIOS password</li>
      <li>Enter and confirm your new password, or leave this blank</li>
      <li>Select the &lsquo;Exit&rsquo; menu</li>
